mixin range-slider(options = {})

    div(class=["range-slider"])
        p(class=["range-slider__title"])
            span(class=["range-slider__slider-name"]) диапазон цены
            span(class=["range-slider__current-values"])
        div(class=["range-slider__content"])
        p(class=["range-slider__description"]) Стоимость за сутки пребывания в номере